title: Mgosoft PDF Spliter SDK
text:
Mgosoft PDF Spliter SDK 
ZDNet Friday 23rd October, 2015 
Mgosoft PDF Spliter is a simple, stand-alone application that lets you split any Acrobat pdf file into smaller PDF files. Mgosoft PDF Spliter provides numerous alternatives for split large PDF file into single pages or save every a few pages as a new file or extract part of a PDF file. Mgosoft PDF Spliter does not require Adobe Acrobat, and produces documents compatible with Adobe Acrobat Reader Version 5 and above.
